        <div class="accordion-body">
            <p class="fs-30 mb-30">Through his research, Dr Pennino discovered Dermafixium, which is a beneficial
                extract from one of the good microbes on the healthy skin of children and adults and is deficient in
                individuals affected by skin disorders like Eczema. Importantly, this microbial strain of Lactobacillus
                behind Dermafixium lives specifically on human skin, unlike the other members in the same family that
                are normally found in the gut.</p>
