                <h5 class="mt-10 fs-30 mb-0">Representative result of SLS induced erythema in 24 hours patch test</h5>
            </div>
            <p class="mt-20 fs-30 mb-0">Dermafixium is a natural source of essential molecules and nutrients for the
                skin, consisting of short-chain fatty acids and microbial metabolites, that promote healthier skin when
                re-introduced onto the skin. Dr Pennino and The SkinBiome Co. team spent close to 10 years developing a
                highly effective formula for people affected by skin disorders. Our scientific data here strongly
                supports that our formulation can lead to visible skin improvement within one day of application.</p>
